<HEADLINE>
FT  16 APR 93 / World News in Brief: Bogota bomb blast
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
At least 15 people were killed and more than 100 injured when a car bomb
exploded in the Colombian capital, Bogota.
</TEXT>
