<HEADLINE>
FT  16 APR 93 / World News in Brief: No penalty
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Private security company Group 4 will not suffer penalties for escapes
during the first week of privatised prisoner escort services, the head of
the prison service said. Moments after he spoke, another prisoner in Group 4
custody escaped from a Derbyshire magistrates' court. Caution over next
contract, Page 11
</TEXT>
