<HEADLINE>
FT  16 APR 93 / World News in Brief: Britons found safe
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Four British climbers and their Russian guide were found safe and well
almost a week after disappearing on Mount Elbrus in the Caucasus. They said
they owed their survival to luck, Mars bars and a cigarette lighter which
enabled them to make fires.
</TEXT>
